Ranger Help for: religious
==========================

SUMMARY:
The Religious branch represents the divine gifts granted to Rangers by
Gaia herself. These powers are rare and demanding, drawing heavily on
the Ranger's spell points, but they can turn the tide of battle or
save a life in desperate moments.

Key religious skills include:

  Meditation          - Restore spell points through communion with nature
  Ceremony            - Perform a ritual to honor Gaia
  Wrath of Gaia       - Powerful nature damage spell
  Winter's Bite       - Cold damage attack channeling winter's fury
  Essence of the Land - Draw power from surrounding terrain for stat buffs
  Seasonal Flux       - Channel the current season's energy into an attack
  Nature's Protection - Create a protective aura reducing incoming damage
  Gaia's Eyes         - Remote viewing of distant rooms
  Gaia's Touch        - Healing touch channeling Gaia's restorative power
  Tap Stone           - Draw spell points from the earth through stone
  Pecking Birds       - Call birds to harass and distract a target
  Gaia Incarnate      - Transform into an avatar of Gaia

These powers are strongest when performed in the Ranger's primary
terrain and weakest when alignment strays from neutral.

